{
  "stem": "293.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have a lot of Polish friends-- tremendous amount of friends-- from the university, from the army, from the school, and, and they were very supporting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Very supporting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything I need something-- so I was smuggling some things like, for example, when somebody need [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] strawberry jam or, or, or juice to make wine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Was a winery in ghetto, because sugar, they couldn't get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I brought him about 50 bottles of it, because I knew somebody who was on the guard with the things and figured how else you could bring them in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You make a living.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was always traveling with a big bag.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the bag you could find anything you want.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, when I-- when I will be caught, I wouldn't be talking to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't think about the danger in this time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was thinking that I'm so smart that I can avoid everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you never know what in the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was sure that I will survive the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] No question about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I will survive the war, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you something, what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a chance to go out anytime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Mila was a little bit scared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember, she was only 20, 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She never live yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She didn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was at least seven years older, and I saw something in my life already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know they were going under false paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew they were going to the border to Czechoslovakia, to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, remember, Mila got one big complex.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was thinking that she looks too Jewish to go out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just tried to persuade her that she doesn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
